{"id":2946,"date":"2017-12-22T02:08:47","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T10:08:47","slug":"hugo-cool-and-the-bag","title":"Hugo Bernatas x Cool &#038; The Bag","content":"<p>We met Hugo in Lyon around Christmas 2014. He was probably one of the very first users of, what was back then, version 0 of the Krak App.</p>\n<p>Coming from and skating in the same city definitely made things easy. We spent the whole evening together, talking about the spots around, our favorite skate videos and random stuff. He was studying but we decided to keep him close and each time we needed a photographer or a filmer based in Lyon we asked him.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_2954\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2954\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2954\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Crooked-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Vincent Veglio, crooked. Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Crooked-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Crooked-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2954\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vincent Veglio, crooked. Photo: Hugo Bernatas</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_2955\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2955\" class=\"wp-image-2955 size-full\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Ollie-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Vincent Veglio, ollie. Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Ollie-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hugo-Vincent-Veglio-Ollie-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2955\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vincent Veglio, ollie. Photo: Hugo Bernatas</p></div>\n<p>We can proudly say 2 things now: we’ve never been disappointed by his amazing skills AND we’ve become friends. So every time we pass by Lyon it’s always a pleasure to hit the streets with him and enjoy local food and drinks.</p>\n<p>He was the one behind the camera for our first ‘Krak session’ and the first ‘Krak interview’ with Chris Chann. You can find these videos on Youtube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/krakskate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">+krakskate</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_2949\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2949\" class=\"wp-image-2949 size-full\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Color-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Color-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/hugo-Color-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hugo-Color-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2949\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo: Hugo Bernatas</p></div>\n<p>We’re stoked now to print some of his favorite photos on <a href=\"https://coolandthebag.com/search?q=hugo+bernatas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this very cool tote-bag</a> from another friend based in Paris: Cool &amp; The Bag. You can find out more about them here: <a href=\"https://coolandthebag.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">coolandthebag.com</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_2956\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2956\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2956\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_break.jpg\" alt=\"Hugo Bernatas x Cool &amp; The Bag Tote\" width=\"300\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_break.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_240/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_break.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2956\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hugo Bernatas x Cool &amp; The Bag Tote</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_2957\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2957\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2957\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_wall_ride.jpg\" alt=\"Hugo Bernatas x Cool &amp; The Bag Tote\" width=\"300\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_wall_ride.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_240/mag/uploads/hugo-tote_bag_wall_ride.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2957\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hugo Bernatas x Cool &amp; The Bag Tote</p></div>\n<p>And if you wanna send some love to Hugo himself —or even better: give him some gigs—you can find this truly passionate guy here:<br />\non the <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Krak App</a>: @hugob<br />\non instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hugobernatas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@hugobernatas</a><br />\non his website: <a href=\"http://hugobernatas.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hugobernatas.com</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_2952\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2952\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2952\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Hugo-Quentin-P-Nose-Bump-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Quentin P, nose bump. Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Hugo-Quentin-P-Nose-Bump-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Hugo-Quentin-P-Nose-Bump-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2952\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quentin P, nose bump. Photo: Hugo Bernatas</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_2953\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2953\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2953\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Street-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Street-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hugo-Street-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2953\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo: Hugo Bernatas</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_2950\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2950\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2950\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Push-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: Hugo Bernatas\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hugo-Push-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hugo-Push-Photo-Hugo-Bernatas.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2950\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo: Hugo Bernata</p></div>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><strong>This feature was originally published in the printed KrakMag that shipped with the European &#8216;Cheers&#8217; <a href=\"https://krakbox.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel